---------------------
How to play the game?
---------------------

1. Go to https://sackarias.se/
2. That's it

-----------------------
How to install and run the code?
-----------------------

1. Install node.js (LTS version) at https://nodejs.org/en/
2. Clone the repo
3. Run "npm install" to install all dependencies
4. Run "npm run dev" to run the code on a local server at http://localhost:3000/
5. And you're done!

----------------------
What code is important in this repo?
----------------------

1. Everything inside /src/. The rest is mostly boilerplate to make the website work
2. A lot of the repo is JSX and styling. Most of the logic is in /src/WOC/WOC.tsx and /src/Game.tsx
3. The connection to the Openweather API is contained in /src/WOC/WOC.tsx
4. The game state and logic is contained in /src/Game.tsx